            Some interpretations I looked up said it was God, some said it might have been a friend or 
            romantic partner, or about the loss of a child. 
            Not sure how much the authorial intent matters, but the abstractions and elisions in this poem also made it 
            a little difficult to mark up. @Caroline and Wyatt, feel free to expand on what I have here-->
        </stanza>
    </body>
</poem>

